# TruffleHog ignore patterns for test files containing mock credentials
# These are test-only mock secrets, not real credentials

# Test directories
**/tests/
**/test/
**/__tests__/

# Specific test files with mock credentials
**/conftest.py
**/test_*.py
**/*_test.py

# Environment files (already tracked in gitignore but adding for clarity)
**/.env.local
**/.env
**/venv/
**/.venv/
**/.pytest_cache/
**/node_modules/

# Documentation
**/README.md
